name: Splashing bath .aif
description:
Some Splashing in a Bath in Bath. Recorded using A Rode Nt1 running through to a  Tascam 1082 into Logic pro 9. Samples where from taking a mug of water and pouring it into a bath full of water. ( after having a bath not to waste the water ) Recorded at December 1st 2014 6:36pm. 
No additional plug-ins or normalisation was used.
